  <section class="container program-about">
    <h3>About the Program</h3>
    <p>The iKhaya Golden Mic Program is NCEP NOMDUVA’s platform for young creatives in acting, writing, and music. Our mission is to identify, develop, and connect South African youth talent with real opportunities in the entertainment and creative industries.</p>
    <p>Through mentorship, workshops, and industry showcases, we equip participants with professional skills, confidence, and networks.</p>
    <p><strong>Vision:</strong> To build the next generation of South African stars who tell our stories and shape our culture.</p>
